{"pageProps":{"post":{"summary":null,"tags":["HTTP"],"id":"web-browser-do-http-request","contentHtml":"<p>介绍一下在浏览器里完成一次网络请求的流程步骤。</p>\n<p>当在浏览器里输入一行网址，并按下回车执行之后，会经过以下几个流程：</p>\n<h1>1. DNS解析</h1>\n<p>将域名解析成IP地址。</p>\n<h1>2. TCP连接</h1>\n<p>TCP三次握手，建立TCP连接。</p>\n<h1>3. HTTP请求</h1>\n<p>发送HTTP请求并获取数据结果。</p>\n<h1>4. 构建DOM树</h1>\n<p>使用HTML字符串构建DOM树。</p>\n<h1>5. 构建CSSOM树</h1>\n<p>使用CSS字符串构建CSSOM树。</p>\n<h1>6. 合成并绘制</h1>\n<p>使用DOM+CSSOM进行渲染，合成并绘制结果。</p>\n","date":"2011-03-02T10:00:00.000Z","title":"浏览器的一次网络请求流程","published":true,"hideInList":false,"feature":null,"isTop":false},"prevPost":{"summary":null,"tags":["数据结构","算法"],"id":"linked-list-intro","title":"数据结构：链表","date":"2011-03-07T10:00:00.000Z","published":true,"hideInList":false,"feature":null,"isTop":false},"nextPost":{"summary":null,"tags":["网络"],"id":"check-ip-port-signal","title":"IP、端口和通信检查","date":"2011-03-02T10:00:00.000Z","published":true,"hideInList":false,"feature":null,"isTop":false}},"__N_SSG":true}